Tango with Me bụ ihe nkiri ihunanya nke Naijiria nke afọ 2010 nke Femi Kayode dere, nke Mahmood Ali-Balogun mebere ma duzie ya ma bụrụ Genevieve Nnaji, Joseph Benjamin na Joke Silva
A họpụtara ihe nkiri a maka ihe nrite ise na 7th Africa Movie Academy Awards
Ihe nkiri ahụ nwetara ezigbo nyocha sitere n'aka ndị nkatọ
Nollywood Forever nyere ya 80% wee dee "Tango with Me ka ejiri ụda egwu nke ọma mepụta ya
Joseph na Genny mara mma ma nwee kemistri dị mfe
Achọpụtara m na ọ dị ntakịrị nwayọ n'akụkụ mana ihe ngosi ahụ nwere oke mmụọ na nke sitere n'obi."
